was just looking at her the way she was on

00:19:46.880 --> 00:19:47.880
Me.

00:19:47.880 --> 00:19:51.190
“My husband might be your husband’s boss”
this and that.

00:19:51.190 --> 00:19:55.020
I said, “Maybe I don’t know anything about
these things.

00:19:55.020 --> 00:19:57.990
I am sorry, I don’t know your list of people,
anything.

00:19:57.990 --> 00:19:59.770
I am not interested.”

00:19:59.770 --> 00:20:02.150
And then My husband came.

00:20:02.150 --> 00:20:03.930
So she said, “See that tall man.

00:20:03.930 --> 00:20:06.430
You know he’s very important.

00:20:06.430 --> 00:20:08.320
He’s with the Prime Minister.

00:20:08.320 --> 00:20:12.570
You go and talk to him and get Your husband
promoted.”

00:20:12.570 --> 00:20:23.900
I said ([Laughing] What is she up to?), I
said, “Sudhali, he is My husband.”

00:20:23.900 --> 00:20:24.900
“Heh!

00:20:24.900 --> 00:20:26.540
He’s your husband?

00:20:26.540 --> 00:20:27.540
Haan yaar!

00:20:27.540 --> 00:20:28.940
Oh my God!

00:20:28.940 --> 00:20:30.870
I am sorry I am.”

00:20:30.870 --> 00:20:33.040
I said, “It’s all right.”

00:20:33.040 --> 00:20:34.040
Common experience.

00:20:34.040 --> 00:20:42.620
The women also become IAS, you see, not actually
but as wives and I’ve been such a lost person

00:20:42.620 --> 00:20:44.680
with them.

00:20:44.680 --> 00:20:50.860
I could never understand what is there to
be IAS and to be his wife.

00:20:50.860 --> 00:20:52.660
It was beyond Me.

00:20:52.660 --> 00:20:59.200
But one thing, what really helped Me in all
this turmoil of life, because you know our

00:20:59.200 --> 00:21:09.880
pay is less, this, that all problems are there,
was the patriotism Raashtra Bhakti.

00:21:09.880 --> 00:21:11.940
My father was a great patriot.

00:21:11.940 --> 00:21:13.100
My mother was.

00:21:13.100 --> 00:21:18.090
They sacrificed everything for the independence
of this country.

00:21:18.090 --> 00:21:23.520
I cannot travel by any foreign airlines, whatever
maybe.

00:21:23.520 --> 00:21:26.220
Maybe Air India is not good, doesn’t matter.

00:21:26.220 --> 00:21:28.550
It’s My, My country’s.

00:21:28.550 --> 00:21:35.480
So the feeling that this is My country kept
Me going.

00:21:35.480 --> 00:21:39.410
You see you become like a Kargil soldier.

00:21:39.410 --> 00:21:42.390
You are fighting for your country.

00:21:42.390 --> 00:21:47.320
You are working for your country.

00:21:47.320 --> 00:21:50.580
My husband got into Indian Foreign Service.

00:21:50.580 --> 00:21:51.920
I told him, “Nothing doing.

00:21:51.920 --> 00:21:56.610
We don’t drink, both of us and I can’t
leave My country in the lurch at the time

00:21:56.610 --> 00:21:58.650
when we have got the freedom.

00:21:58.650 --> 00:22:01.100
So if you want you can go, I will not come.

00:22:01.100 --> 00:22:03.260
I don’t want to go to Foreign Service.”

