They cut his pay.

00:22:04.700 --> 00:22:07.510
That time, you know, 300 was a big amount.

00:22:07.510 --> 00:22:09.130
I said, “Doesn’t matter.

00:22:09.130 --> 00:22:11.150
Whatever it is, I’ll stay in My country.

00:22:11.150 --> 00:22:13.640
I’ll work in My country and you work here.

00:22:13.640 --> 00:22:16.150
I’ll support you every way.

00:22:16.150 --> 00:22:18.830
I don’t want anything.

00:22:18.830 --> 00:22:25.740
Nothing I want and you don’t take a bribe
at all otherwise that day I’ll leave this.”

00:22:25.740 --> 00:22:33.650
Otherwise also I said that, “The another
thing is our country has to develop.”

00:22:33.650 --> 00:22:36.660
Who will develop?

00:22:36.660 --> 00:22:41.210
I always felt that you are the spinal cord
of our country.

00:22:41.210 --> 00:22:43.420
You have to develop this country.

00:22:43.420 --> 00:22:44.420
What is this money?

00:22:44.420 --> 00:22:45.420
Comes and goes.

00:22:45.420 --> 00:22:50.800
You’ve seen the people who have got money,
where their children have gone?

00:22:50.800 --> 00:22:53.360
What has happened to them?

00:22:53.360 --> 00:22:54.360
What have they achieved?

00:22:54.360 --> 00:22:59.080
So I told very frankly that I will not go
to the Foreign Service of any kind because

00:22:59.080 --> 00:23:00.720
what is in the Foreign Service?

00:23:00.720 --> 00:23:06.760
I want to do everything in this country of
Mine for which I have also fought.

00:23:06.760 --> 00:23:14.150
I have fought a lot and this is what now sometimes,
you know, is disappointing to see what things

00:23:14.150 --> 00:23:15.240
are happening.

