Because when this happens, when this Kundalini
rising take place, when people become realized

00:23:24.950 --> 00:23:27.470
souls, they just transform.

00:23:27.470 --> 00:23:35.040
They become extremely patriotic, extremely
patriotic and they understand what is needed

00:23:35.040 --> 00:23:37.340
today for our country.

