They can sacrifice anything.

00:23:39.280 --> 00:23:48.240
They can live anywhere and they are not bothered
about some sort of a, you can call it a financial

00:23:48.240 --> 00:23:51.070
help or other material thing.

00:23:51.070 --> 00:23:53.330
They are above materialism.

00:23:53.330 --> 00:24:01.250
There are thousands and thousands like that
even in our country, thousands and also abroad.

